    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is ideal for a dedicated project or as a donor for parts. The engine runs very roughly with a likely head gasket failure and significant oil leaks, and the transmission shifts harshly between gears. The body shows heavy rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, while the interior has torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. It starts and moves, but it is not roadworthy and will need to be towed.",
      "price": 3000.0,
