    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a peerless example of automotive excellence, preserved in showroom condition. This vehicle has been curated with fastidious attention to detail, manifesting in an immaculate exterior and a pristine, smoke-free interior. Mechanically, the car performs with the precision of a new factory delivery, having undergone rigorous multi-point verification. This is a definitive acquisition for the individual who demands nothing less than perfection.",
